{"tid":635562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【奪命車禍】死者為Uber司機 Uber︰對家屬深切慰問","createTime":"2018-04-20T08:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T10:24:18.000Z","uid":47272,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd1c31201178bd20c8a75546270b20d266d7ceb","tid":635562,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:28:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180420&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58096688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180420%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58096688&d=7BieEHDRrS%2FIJH8FDuFIajA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e81cb98a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180420%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58096688&h=deccff07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180420&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58096688</a><br />\n旺角亞皆老街昨晚發生1死2危殆車禍，死者為寶馬司機，他證實是Uber的司機夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n50歲Uber司機，昨晚駕駛寶馬房車接載女乘客途中遇車禍，失控越過對面線與的士迎頭相撞，釀成4車「串燒」。Uber司機傷重身亡，Uber女乘客與及被撞的士司機和女乘客全部受傷。<br />\n<br />\n男死者姓許，也是肇事寶馬的車主。《蘋果》致電死者家人，一名女親友表示不欲回應。而Uber查詢時確認，車禍涉及一名Uber司機夥伴及一名Uber乘客。Uber對於意外感到非常傷感，並向司機夥伴的家庭作出深切慰問，亦已聯絡受傷的Uber乘客作出協助。Uber表示，已按《汽車保險 ( 第三者風險 ) 條例》 ( 第 272 章 )的規定，為所有香港的 Uber 車程安排第三方保險。<br />\n<br />\n事發於昨晚9時左右，許駕駛寶馬房車載着姓周女乘客(39歲)，沿亞皆老街天橋往旺角，至中電對開時，懷疑失控越過對面線，與駛至的士迎頭相撞。尾隨的士的七人車及電單車也收掣不及，相繼撞上。除了許及周女乘客外，姓梁的士司機(60歲)、姓梁女乘客(32歲)及姓劉鐵騎士(39歲)也告受傷。當中的士司機及女乘客情況危殆，周女情況穩定，鐵騎士無大礙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4paz3td7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4paz3td7&h=e4e246c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e204d6a34f4ce45664adccd0d09e70cefebdb1f","tid":635562,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知有無得賠"},{"pid":"e46fce9e90644ea93c15a9f3bc63d069ef6463ff","tid":635562,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"好多d 天橋好恐怖, 雙線來回, 無分隔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同對面線hi 少少已經係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d538e049b4a6625c9cd777629e2c2f6659d832e","tid":635562,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18e4201ef76da49b0200169d15d4a81be4a62ba","tid":635562,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e46fce9e90644ea93c15a9f3bc63d069ef6463ff","tid":635562,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"好多d 天橋好恐怖, 雙線來回, 無分隔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同對面線hi 少少已經係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T09:06:42.000Z","msg":"無形的壓力，對面仲要鬼咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1685c1f510d3de8cba20fd9937b41f79cc5bfc","tid":635562,"uid":17405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"車無事，人死左？"},{"pid":"f8a987b7ee05ab76b4593b978365f266e0a50785","tid":635562,"uid":87120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T09:30:04.000Z","msg":"可能撞擊力大， 2 邊都行 70 ， 對撞實好甘...."},{"pid":"d5ac99df87896f855fed43e315baec1b6e602be6","tid":635562,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f18e4201ef76da49b0200169d15d4a81be4a62ba","tid":635562,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e46fce9e90644ea93c15a9f3bc63d069ef6463ff","tid":635562,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"好多d 天橋好恐怖, 雙線來回, 無分隔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同對面線hi 少少已經係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T09